title: Cinema.Craft.Encoder.SP2.v1.00.00.18-iND
description:
CCE-SP2 allows you to directly Encode AVI, QuickTime and DV files
   into DVD compliant high-quality MPEG-2 streams. CCE-SP2 is the
       ideal tool for creating MPEG-2 streams for non-liner video
                      editors, 3DCG animators, and game creators.


www: http://www.cinemacraft.com/eng/sp2.html


notes: unpack, install, copy patch to install dir and run it.
